<body>
<header>
    {% set pageName = 'Our Story' %}
    {% include "components/header.twig" %}
</header>


<div id="our-story">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="page-title">
                <h1>Our Story</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="page-title">
                <a href="https://dealmirror.com/">
                    <img src="https://assets.ratemyservice.io/images/Dealmirror_join_RMS4.webp">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <p>
                Here is our <a href="https://dealmirror.com/product/rate-my-service-lifetime-deal/">success story</a>
                with Shivam and <a href="https://dealmirror.com/">Dealmirror</a>.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>
                Our journey took an exciting turn when we crossed paths with Shivam, a friendly and resourceful member of the Dealmirror team. Recognizing the immense potential of collaborating with him, we eagerly joined forces. With his expertise and guidance, we successfully launched our product on Dealmirror, opening the doors to a world of opportunities.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>
                Dealmirror proved to be an extraordinary platform with an incredible audience base, and Shivam played a pivotal role in introducing our product to their vibrant community, particularly on Facebook. Through his strategic promotions and compelling introductions, our product swiftly gained traction and captured the attention of enthusiastic users who were eagerly awaiting its arrival.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>
                Expressing our heartfelt gratitude, we extend our deepest appreciation to both Dealmirror and Shivam for their unwavering support. Their belief in our product and the assistance they provided throughout the journey were instrumental in its resounding success. Inspired by this triumph, we are excited to continue our collaboration with Dealmirror, bringing forth more innovative tools that will further enrich their platform.
            </p>
            <br>
            <p>
                Kind regards,
                <br>
                Dominic Meulemans
                <br>
                CEO/Founder
                <br>
                RateMyService
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    {% include "components/footer.twig" %}
</footer>
</body>
</html>

